    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异界的剑与魔法篇章</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家被神秘的力量召唤至一场血与暗的阴谋里，在波澜壮阔的中土奇幻世界——沃尼米尔中，以英雄王的预言指引，你将踏上拯救世界与携手伙伴的奇幻冒险！集结队友，击退暗流势力，逐步揭示世界的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《《崛起力量: 沃尼米尔》 是一款结合精致的高清晰度像素风格，爽快动作化战斗体验，和中世纪奇幻冒险的动作角色扮演游戏，也是《崛起力量》系列的全新进化之作，在进一步深化战斗系统的基础上，增加了丰富的故事剧情，以及探索与冒险。 <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/785f5f985ef6e00a37a31a9b031f4f9f.poster.avif?t=1765611531\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/785f5f985ef6e00a37a31a9b031f4f9f.webm?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/785f5f985ef6e00a37a31a9b031f4f9f.mp4?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/80aa76aa119e3c690b40d901abae61f8.poster.avif?t=1765611531\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/80aa76aa119e3c690b40d901abae61f8.webm?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/80aa76aa119e3c690b40d901abae61f8.mp4?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>爽快的战斗</strong>，精心打磨的动作系统，包括闪避、重击、反擊、拼刀、终结攻击、精准系统、取消等机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>八种武器模组</strong>，匕首、长剑、巨剑、太刀、长枪、弓箭、法杖、拳套，每种自带丰富的派生技与武技系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略深度丰富</strong>，可即时切换队友，队友连携，精准切换，奥丁大招，鸦灵系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备技能自由更换，</strong>通用天赋树可重置，搭配角色专属能力，发掘不同组合的游玩乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紧张刺激的Boss战，</strong>Boss 拥有多阶段战斗、反击、投技、防御机制，甚至能发动毁灭性的连招或合体攻击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>旅途技能</strong>，偷窃、决斗、侦察，破坏隐藏封印，发掘宝藏，体验探索的乐趣。  \t</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精美像素风</strong>，从村庄到城堡，从荒漠到冰原，体验如画般的立体风景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式环境</strong>，许多城镇变化分清晨、早上、中午、下午、傍晚、夜晚的动态变化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>命运的故事</strong>，逐步揭露被卷入异界阴谋的穿越者的命运，以及沃尼米尔世界的走向 <br>        </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>信赖的伙伴</strong>，救助与招募队友，为他搭配装备与技能，锻炼他成为你战队中专属战力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>旅途调味剂</strong>，除了各类支线外，还有酒馆、锻造、附魔、合成、分解等活动。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护和平的远古家族卷入惊天阴谋，仅存的继承人奥瑞莉亚也陷入必死的僵局，来自现代的穿越者迪鲁斯临危受命，成为唯一的希望！你，即是世界的英雄！名为英雄王的预言指向故事的主角，为了生存与洗清罪名，加入了探寻英雄王的下落与复兴要塞的征途，与奥瑞莉亚以及来自不同阵营的同伴并肩而行的伙伴们一同踏上征程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/cf363befdb6eb6487245e1687fa96880.poster.avif?t=1765611531\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/cf363befdb6eb6487245e1687fa96880.webm?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/cf363befdb6eb6487245e1687fa96880.mp4?t=1765611531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/33e6953a68a6c26b2d814564787d864b.avif?t=1765611531\" width=616 height=340 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/5351afd428e064f997fbc0fc52c7d610.avif?t=1765611531\" width=616 height=340 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359660/extras/bb4624a7c94b8c986d25f2170591f9d7.avif?t=1765611531\" width=616 height=334 /></span></p></li></ul>",
